snippet.title: Walkabout Mini Golf - Official Spring 2023 Update Trailer | Meta Quest Gaming Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Take a peek at what’s coming to Walkabout Mini Golf, including the second Jules Verne adaptation course, Journey to the Center of the Earth, available on June 8. Additionally, the trailer also reveals the new Evil Lairs series coming in July featuring a bonus Exploding Kittens foxhunt by Elan Lee, and a peek at Pocket Edition for iOS with crossplay for Meta Quest coming late summer.

#GameTrailers #VR
